  Apache Shindig is distributed under the {{{license.html} Apache License, version 2.0}}.

  <Shindig is a distributed as API and as a Web application. You must have a Servlet container for the Java version
  or a Web server for the PHP version installed in order to proceed. Shindig was successfully tested on Jetty (Java),
